Event contract
The primary provisioning event is COGNITO_CREATE. Producer systems send a JSON message describing the target environment, naming, hosted UI domain, admin user, redirect behavior, and optional machine-to-machine configuration.



{
  "action": "COGNITO_CREATE",
  "env": "dev",
  "companyCode": "acme",
  "client": "acme-web-client",
  "domain": "acme-dev-auth",
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@acme.com",
  "callbackUrls": ["https://app.acme.com/callback"],
  "logoutUrls": ["https://app.acme.com/logout"],
  "defaultRedirectUrl": "https://app.acme.com/callback",
  "m2mClient": "acme-m2m-client",
  "scopes": ["read", "write"]
}
