usernames

Array of usernames whose access should be disabled

reason

Optional operational reason for audit or downstream response handling

User deletion event
Use USER_DELETE to permanently delete one or more users. The payload does not require userPoolId; the worker resolves the target user pool from env and companyCode.



{
  "action": "USER_DELETE",
  "env": "dev",
  "companyCode": "acme",
  "usernames": [
