Summary
The Cognito Worker Service provides a strong production-oriented foundation for asynchronous Cognito automation on Kubernetes. It combines event-driven processing, secure RabbitMQ communication, Cognito provisioning, OAuth configuration, and Prometheus-based observability in a single worker service.

Event-driven processing through RabbitMQ

AWS Cognito automation for provisioning and user operations

AWS access through IAM user cognito_user using access key, secret key, and a proper least-privilege IAM policy

